descriptionHtml:
Adds new fruits and recipes.

Recipes include:
Hot Drinks
Juices
Doughnuts
Pancakes
Pies
Tarts
Marmalades
Sausages and Eggs
Toast

Adds ingredient:
Sugar

Foods are in their own leveled lists that are added to merchant chests.

Credits for meshes and textures:

[url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/69637]BRG the Gourmet [/url]by Borgiak
[url=https://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/28091/?]Resource Extra Food v2[/url] by bfadragon
